The Corruptor;;1999;;R;;Action,Crime,Thriller;;6.1;;James Foley;;Chow Yun-Fat,Mark Wahlberg,Ric Young,Paul Ben-Victor,Jon Kit Lee,Andrew Pang,Elizabeth Lindsey,Brian Cox,Byron Mann,Kim Chan,Bill MacDonald,Susie Trinh,Ho Chow,Olivia Yap,Lynda Chiu,Marie Matiko,Pak-Kwong Ho,Tim Progosh;;Nick Chen is one of New York City's most martial police officers and the first Chinese-born immigrant on the force. Chen's job is to keep the peace in Chinatown from a turf war that has broken out between the Triads and the ruthless, and dangerous Fukienese Dragons. Chen teams up with Danny Wallace, who is terribly unaware of this situation. When the Tongs boldly attempt to bribe Wallace, Chen is forced to keep his faithfulness.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0142192/